text: :bulb: HubDB has a location column, so *can we get a location fieldType for custom objects?*

Would love to see more upvotes on this, it's a pretty simple idea that would be quite beneficial from a user experience perspective. <https://community.HubSpot.com/t5/HubSpot-Ideas/Export-form-submissions-filtered-by-date/idi-p/179208>
